**&quot;Litokoala kanunkaensis&quot;
* Genus &quot;Lumakoala&quot;
**&quot;Lumakoala blackae&quot;
* Genus &quot;Koobor&quot;
**&quot;Koobor jimbarrati&quot;
**&quot;Koobor notabilis&quot;
* Genus &quot;Perikoala&quot;
**&quot;Perikoala palankarinnica&quot;
**&quot;Perikoala robustus&quot;
