=== Other honors ===
In 2011, President Michel Martelly of Haiti awarded Jean with the National Order of Honour and Merit to the rank of Grand Officer &quot;as a sign of high consideration national for his dedication to the promotion of Haiti around the world.&quot;

In 2017, Jean was inducted into the New Jersey Hall of Fame.

